Join over 200 volunteers and network with 25 community vendors at the 2015 Big Idea Emporium!

Enjoy breakout sessions covering the following four topics:

1) Diversity & Inclusion presented by UNF Resource Center

2) Communication/Media Workshop, presented by Shepherd Agency

3) New Leader Orientation presented by Girl Scout Trainer, Jacquie Kee

4) How to Create a STEM Experience, presented by TBA

PLUS: preview the Fall Product Sale, re-register your girls or sign-up new girls, volunteers & parents, visit with council Archivist, Patricia Knowles, to take a look at Girl Scouts throughout the years & incorporate GS history at your events/meetings!
